{"TopicId":166326,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Self Destruct?","CreatedByName":"dvp","CreatedById":181270,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T19:18:47Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"dvp","CreatedById":181270,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T19:18:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can delete ships in the tracking center, and I can destroy parts with the right \u0022accidents\u0022 but...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr is that too sadistic?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T19:26:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd that is a good idea because...?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"dvp","CreatedById":181270,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T20:20:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nScreenshots of ships exploding, mostly.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, it might be nice to be able to \u0027[\u0027 or \u0027]\u0027 through local debris and clean it up quickly without having to go back to the tracking center.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-09T20:20:51Z\u0022 title=\u002210/09/2017 08:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 9, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by dvp\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T21:03:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223190673\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022166326\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221507580414\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022181270\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022dvp\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n33 minutes ago, dvp said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, it might be nice to be able to \u0027[\u0027 or \u0027]\u0027 through local debris and clean it up quickly without having to go back to the tracking center.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, that would be useful. But I\u0027d be a bit worried about the self-destruct button\u00A0 being close to more prosaic options\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"juanml82","CreatedById":105344,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T21:50:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s a good idea. Nowadays that means going to the tracking center (loading screen) and making sure you\u0027re deleting the right ships with a two step verification process. A self destruct button somewhere would be a lot more agile.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPlus explosions\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Rocket In My Pocket","CreatedById":154640,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-09T23:12:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAsk, and you shall receive!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed2728939476\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/154232-13-tac-self-destruct-continued/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:227px;max-width:500px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Matuchkin","CreatedById":135127,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T00:33:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo ipsEmbeddedVideo_limited\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022270\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/uhBHL3v4d3I?feature=oembed\u0022 width=\u0022480\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJames Hetfield is a well-known demolitions expert, and specialises in systems of self-destruction in vehicles and facilities. You should go ask him. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAnd yes, I know this comment is completely stupid and out of context, it\u0027s just that, whenever a sentence or phrase is said in average conversation, I instantly hear the song associated with it. Can\u0027t resist.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-10T00:35:01Z\u0022 title=\u002210/10/2017 12:35  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Matuchkin\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"UranianBlue","CreatedById":174952,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T17:57:06Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nDon\u0027t worry!!! Given the right amount of time, anybody can compile a simple C# module that allows for random self-destruct. Then, using some stuff involving ModuleManager, you can add the module to every stock part! However, somebody has already done that, so I won\u0027t try to make a competing mod.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Ultimate Steve","CreatedById":161505,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T18:16:36Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223190716\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022166326\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221507583004\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166502\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Spricigo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n21 hours ago, Spricigo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, that would be useful. But I\u0027d be a bit worried about the self-destruct button\u00A0 being close to more prosaic options\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike ALT\u002BF5 (named quicksave) being right next to ALT\u002BF4 (close the current window)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003ESO MANY TIMES!!!! GRRRR!!!!!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Piatzin","CreatedById":166940,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T18:24:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI just strap a few bombs (from BDAc) to the interior of the ship and activate them whenever I want a big explosion that will take out everything near the craft\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot that it has\u00A0happened. Totally didn\u0027t do forty-seven consecutive tests on various locations. Lies. All of them.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T18:53:45Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust spam the spacebar.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DAL59","CreatedById":180784,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T19:07:38Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPress alt-12 and arm the object thrower.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Mrcarrot","CreatedById":176291,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T19:30:04Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223191426\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022166326\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221507662458\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022180784\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022DAL59\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n22 minutes ago, DAL59 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPress alt-12 and arm the object thrower.\u00A0\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlt\u002BF12.\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:wink:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_wink.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:wink:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-10-10T19:30:19Z\u0022 title=\u002210/10/2017 07:30  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EOctober 10, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by Mrcarrot\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spricigo","CreatedById":166502,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-10-10T23:08:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223191376\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022166326\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221507659396\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161505\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Ultimate Steve\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 hours ago, Ultimate Steve said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike ALT\u002BF5 (named quicksave) being right next to ALT\u002BF4 (close the current window)?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:8px;\u0022\u003ESO MANY TIMES!!!! GRRRR!!!!!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLike SHIFT\u002BTAB\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:mad:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_angry.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:mad:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOr one of the buttons on context menu.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}